    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 Carrera 4S (996.2) offers a visceral driving experience, featuring the 3.6L flat-six powerplant with VarioCam Plus timing. The wide-body chassis utilizes the Turbo-spec suspension geometry and monoblock four-piston calipers for superior braking modulation. Power is delivered through a 6-speed G96 manual transaxle and a viscous multi-plate AWD system, ensuring exceptional mechanical grip. This example has been properly maintained with an LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh clutch assembly. While it exhibits minor road patina typical of a seasoned driver, the hydraulic steering feedback and throttle response are precise. It is a mechanically sound, high-performance machine ready for the canyons.",
